properties.Name: VendorShipmentMethod
properties.Description:
The shipment parameters associated with a Vendor for the indicated period defined by:

- Shipment Method
- Carrier

Columns.Name: VendorId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Vendor.

Columns.Name: ShipmentMethodId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Shipment Method.

Columns.Name: CarrierId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Carrier.

Columns.Name: PreferenceId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Preference.

Columns.Name: PeriodStartDate
Columns.Description: The period start date for which the associated Vendor shipment method information is defined.

Columns.Name: PeriodEndDate
Columns.Description: The period end date for which the associated Vendor shipment method information is defined.

Columns.Name: VendorShipmentMethodNote
Columns.Description: A note, comment or additional information regarding the associated Vendor shipment method.
